ate\\r\\n\\r\\n* **uTLS**: bundled library updated to v1.8.2 for Chrome120 imitation profile identification.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Fixes\\r\\n* avoid DNS leakage with gRPC transports by @leo9800 in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3587\\r\\n* Dynamic address length calculation in shadowsocks udp encoding in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3588\\r\\n\\r\\n## Chores\\r\\n* Chore: bump golang.org/x/crypto from 0.46.0 to 0.47.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3595\\r\\n* Chore: bump golang.org/x/net from 0.48.0 to 0.49.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3594\\r\\n* Chore: bump github.com/miekg/dns from 1.1.69 to 1.1.70 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3592\\r\\n\\r\\n## New Contributors\\r\\n* @leo9800 made their first contribution in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3587\\r\\n\\r\\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/compare/v5.43.0...v5.44.0\",\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/276752429/reactions\",\"total_count\":18,\"+1\":4,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":2,\"hooray\":3,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":3,\"rocket\":4,\"eyes\":2},\"mentions_count\":2},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/273984418\",\"assets_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/273984418/assets\",\"upload_url\":\"https://uploads.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/273984418/assets{?name,label}\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/tag/v5.43.0\",\"id\":273984418,\"author\":{\"login\":\"xiaokangwang\",\"id\":1883569,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjE4ODM1Njk=\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1883569?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/xiaokangwang\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/xiaokangwang\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/xiaokangwang/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/