/v5.39.0\",\"zipball_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/zipball/v5.39.0\",\"body\":\"This is a maintenance release.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Chores\\r\\n* CI: fix stale.yml workflow by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3491\\r\\n* CI: only run release workflow when changing release.yml file by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3492\\r\\n* Fix: geoip test by pinning geoip.dat to specific version by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3495\\r\\n* Chore: bump github.com/go-chi/chi/v5 from 5.2.2 to 5.2.3 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3488\\r\\n* Chore: bump github.com/stretchr/testify from 1.10.0 to 1.11.1 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3487\\r\\n* Chore: bump google.golang.org/protobuf from 1.36.6 to 1.36.8 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3483\\r\\n* Chore: bump google.golang.org/grpc from 1.74.2 to 1.75.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3482\\r\\n* Chore: bump golang.org/x/net from 0.42.0 to 0.43.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3471\\r\\n* Chore: bump github.com/miekg/dns from 1.1.67 to 1.1.68 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3466\\r\\n* Chore: bump actions/stale from 8 to 10 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3501\\r\\n* Chore: bump actions/download-artifact from 4 to 5 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3467\\r\\n* CI: upgrade CodeQL from v2 to v3 by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3507\\r\\n* Docs: update goreportcard badge by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3508\\r\\n* CI: bump actions/checkout from v3 to v5 by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3509\\r\\n* CI: bump actions/setup-go to v6 & use go version in go.mod by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3510\\r\\n* CI: remove unnecessary version option in golangci-lint workflow by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3514\\r\\n* CI: fix test and test coverage by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3515\\r\\n* CI: only upload coverage report on Linux by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3516\\r\\n* Docs: fix badges by @Loyalsoldier in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3517\\r\\n* Chore: bump google.golang.org/grpc from 1.75.0 to 1.75.1 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3519\\r\\n* Chore: bump golang.org/x/net from 0.43.0 to 0.44.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3513\\r\\n* Chore: bump google.golang.org/protobuf from 1.36.8 to 1.36.9 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3512\\r\\n* ci: annotate arm64 pie binary with prerelease mark in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3521\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/compare/v5.38.0...v5.39.0\",\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/247028204/reactions\",\"total_count\":32,\"+1\":11,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":4,\"hooray\":6,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":4,\"rocket\":3,\"eyes\":4},\"mentions_count\":2},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/235379856\",\"assets_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/235379856/assets\",\"upload_url\":\"https://uploads.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/235379856/assets{?name,label}\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/tag/v5.38.0\",\"id\":235379856,\"author\":{\"login\":\"xiaokangwang\",\"id\":1883569,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjE4ODM1Njk=\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1883569?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/xiaokangwang\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/xiaokangwang\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.co