.25.1\",\"zipball_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/zipball/v5.25.1\",\"body\":\"## New Features\\r\\n* Subscription: Add support for URLLine format subscription container.\\r\\n* Subscription: Add gRPC API support.\\r\\n* (Preview) Add WebUI Support in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3284\\r\\n  * The associated in browser web interface project has not been released yet.\\r\\n\\r\\n## Fixes\\r\\n* Fix broken pie build with generating separate files in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3281\\r\\n* Really fix pie build in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3286\\r\\n* Fix panic in observatory's grpc command when incorrect tag are supplied. \\r\\n\\r\\n## Chore\\r\\n* Resync Hysteria2 Import in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3280\\r\\n* Chore: bump google.golang.org/protobuf from 1.35.2 to 1.36.3 by @dependabot in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3285\\r\\n* Chore: bump google.golang.org/grpc from 1.68.1 to 1.69.4 by @dependabot in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3283\\r\\n* Chore: bump github.com/go-playground/validator/v10 from 10.22.1 to 10.24.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3282\\r\\n* Chore: bump github.com/go-chi/chi/v5 from 5.1.0 to 5.2.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3261\\r\\n* Chore: bump github.com/stretchr/testify from 1.9.0 to 1.10.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/pull/3236\\r\\n\\r\\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/v2fly/v2ray-core/compare/v5.24.0...v5.25.1\",\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/195876885/reactions\",\"total_count\":18,\"+1\":5,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":2,\"hooray\":4,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":3,\"rocket\":2,\"eyes\":2},\"mentions_count\":1},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/195458197\",\"assets_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/v2fly/v2ray-core/releases/195458197/assets\",\"upload_url\":\"https://uploads.github.co